channel.description:
Hello this is my old client i released this because i am using a new 1.
This is my first real client release.
LINK: http://www.megaupload.com/?d=U7CCYPTU
Credits: GamerX 70% for base i didnt so much Me 25% for updating demise 5% for His glitched cache......
It has The following. Hovering tabs 100% perfect sideicons Class9.java is Cleaned NO 1 INTERFACE you need to add your own. class8 is ripped from my older client :P it has Much new items no custom ones like dragon g and lemon That Sucks! Godsword stance mouse scroller No Lagg 508 models in the cache (From Demise) Glitched ass hell womans are fking glitched the monsters with shield are glitched and some weapons Just replace cache with yours Srry if i release me new client it has no glitch -.-. the cache has new hitmark and equiq sorites custom ones Not very nice but it sin the cache. and new head arrows npcs are 25% 508 By Demises cache. removed some junk files. And ehm it has some interface sprites i didnt remove my interface sprites :Z Buts its nice for beginners i dont care if you flame.. it has about/website/sip button on client background but gamerx added it :p It Has a taskbar icon
For more infomation/questions add me msn icarepkz@live.nl
Pictures: (if you want to see the pictures now just download the folder with pics here:http://www.megaupload.com/?d=KVHYLJ85 ) [u][i][b]IF SOME PICTURES NOT DISPLAY CLICK THE WEBSITE UNDER IT[/b][/i][/u] (Login) [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/9puov8.jpg[/img] http://i46.tinypic.com/9puov8.jpg (About) [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/x5rqfm.jpg[/img] http://i48.tinypic.com/x5rqfm.jpg (new equiq and models) [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/2e4vgbc.jpg[/img] http://i49.tinypic.com/2e4vgbc.jpg (Close login) [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/fp8bx4.jpg[/img] http://i45.tinypic.com/fp8bx4.jpg (hitmarks) [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/14b8gtc.jpg[/img] http://i48.tinypic.com/14b8gtc.jpg (Hd npcs) [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/2u8fofc.jpg[/img] http://i46.tinypic.com/2u8fofc.jpg

Replace your class20, class36, class23.java with this ones: http://www.mediafire.com/?tm2jgzddd5t And in cache317 Add a folder called anims and put this in it: http://www.mediafire.com/?dzzhjj25yzw Just replace you exist .dat files with that ones in winrar folder others you have not New animations and client will not startup ;)
_________________________ THIS TUT HAS 1 ANTILEECH!| _________________________ Done you have now new karils bow, whip, gd specs, barrelchest anchor,godwars npc animations~! And extending emote,animation list and extending gfx list ;)
!!!!!Now for new models!!!!! Those are not 508 character models only some items are 508 377 and 317
Credits for this animations: Swat 80% for emote system and animation config. demise 19 % for some animations and me 1% for adding then to client ;P
Replace class8.java with this 1: http://www.mediafire.com/?cnokwmmmwtn replace your models with this 1: http://www.mediafire.com/?nnynlmxwm1z
Credits for this models,class8.java Class8.java is from the client download but added very much ints and deleted custom ones. models From Forums So 95% to the guys/girls that made or released the models 5% for me for adding
